<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-off-to">be off to</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>动身去</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tomorrow we are off to Naples to visit the museum that houses many of the treasures from Pompeii.
明天我们将出发去那不勒斯参观博物馆，那里收藏了许多庞贝珍品。</p><footer>译林③ – 3</footer></div></div>